# ==========================================
# CHANGELOG
# v1.0.0 (2026-04-15)
# - Initial creation for RuoYi (Spring Boot + Vue3) framework to optimize Trae AI indexing.
# - Added exclusions for Maven/Node build artifacts, IDE caches, and common logs.
# - Added specific exclusions for RuoYi modules (ruoyi-admin, ruoyi-common, ruoyi-ui, etc.).
# - Excluded local sensitive configurations (application-*.yml) to prevent secret leaks and hallucinations.
# ==========================================

# ==========================================
# 1. 通用排除项 (General Exclusions)
# ==========================================
# 操作系统隐藏文件与缓存
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
*.bak
*.tmp
tmp/
temp/

# IDE 缓存与配置 (IDEA, VSCode, Eclipse 等)
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.settings/
.project
.classpath
.lingma/

# 日志与构建监控产物
*.log
logs/
hs_err_pid*
replay_pid*

# ==========================================
# 2. 后端 Spring Boot 模块 (Backend Spring Boot)
# ==========================================
# 编译输出目录 (Build Artifacts)
# 排除所有的 target 编译结果目录，杜绝 AI 索引重复的 .class 文件
target/
!ruoyi-*/target/classes/  # 取消特定保留，通常后端直接全忽略
ruoyi-admin/target/
ruoyi-common/target/
ruoyi-framework/target/
ruoyi-system/target/
ruoyi-quartz/target/
ruoyi-generator/target/

# 打包产物
*.jar
*.war
*.ear
*.class

# 本地敏感配置与密钥 (Sensitive Local Configs)
# 排除带有具体敏感配置的环境文件（如数据库密码、Redis密钥、JWT Token等），保留 application.yml 做结构参考
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-dev.yml
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-prod.yml

# ==========================================
# 3. 前端 Vue3 模块 (Frontend Vue3)
# ==========================================
# 依赖包 (Dependencies)
# 必须排除 node_modules，否则会导致海量无用索引
RuoYi-Vue3/node_modules/

# 构建产物 (Build Outputs)
# 排除 Webpack/Vite 编译打包后的生产环境文件
RuoYi-Vue3/dist/
RuoYi-Vue3/build/
dist/

# 包管理缓存与日志 (Package Manager Caches & Logs)
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.pnpm-store/
.npm/

# [ruoyi-generator] 代码生成器产物
# 排除生成的临时 ZIP 压缩包或自动生成的代码草稿，避免污染当前业务逻辑上下文
ruoyi-generator/src/main/resources/vm/*.zip
*.zip

# 数据库脚本或大文件 (Database Scripts & Large Files)
# 若依自带的 SQL 初始化文件仅供执行，不需要长期保留在 AI 上下文中进行语义分析
sql/
*.sql
*.pdf

# vue2版本已弃用
ruoyi-ui/